{"books":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":[""],"article":{"title":"大字报——交响诗","authors":["中央音乐学院学生","苏三"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":6}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"text":"大字报——交响诗","type":"title"},{"text":"中央音乐学院学生苏三","type":"authors"},{"text":"序曲","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"(一) 煑豆燃豆箕，豆在锅中泣；同是爱国者，何必煑太急；","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(二) 话堪说时直需说，莫待无人空吱吱。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"第一乐章","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"津门之疆兮土飞扬，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"烟雾拢照兮渺茫茫，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"奇矣仓库兮音乐府，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"弦外之音兮凄怆怆。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"第二乐章","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"解放八年兮运动重重，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"大张旗鼓兮雷厉风行，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"今朝整风兮和风细雨，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"宇宙干坤兮群众呼声，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"爱党爱国兮尔吾有分，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"助党整风兮重放光明。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"第三乐章","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"金冠玉带兮紫罗袍，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"逢迎献媚兮乌纱帽，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"庶民疾苦兮有望日，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"党召整风兮春放光。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":" 来源：1957年6月7日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","type":"paragraph"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":0,"page_end":0,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}